Pathway explored : REACTOME TRANSCRIPTION COUPLED NUCLEOTIDE EXCISION REPAIR TC NER

This pathway contain 78 genes.

In these 78 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
